#F  CheckForHandlingByNiceBasis( <R>, <gens>, <M>, <zero> )
##
##  <#GAPDoc Label="CheckForHandlingByNiceBasis">
##  <ManSection>
##  <Func Name="CheckForHandlingByNiceBasis" Arg='R, gens, M, zero'/>
##
##  <Description>
